column2: Collection in progress by Jeremy Pressman (@djpressman, U of Connecticut) and Erica Chenoweth (@EricaChenoweth, U of Denver).
With thanks to Rivera Sun, Sarah Syverson, David Luchs, & many others for assistance compiling sources.
We are not collecting this data as part of a research project. We are doing this in the public interest. We are not affiliated with any other efforts to collect data on the demonstrations.
UPDATE (5:04 pm EST, Jan 26): We are no longer accepting additional information. Thank you.
